{"article_id":"v9IiY1uxsNWBwqFe","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Justice Department 's seizure of phone records for journalists at the Associated Press is hurting the agency 's ability","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"to gather news ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"the wire service 's Chief Executive and President Gary Pruitt said on Sunday .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"`` Officials","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"that would normally talk to us","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"and people","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"we talk to in the normal course of news gathering","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"are already saying to us","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"that they 're a little reluctant to talk to us , ''","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Pruitt said on CBS 's `` Face The Nation '' program .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"`` They fear","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"that they will be monitored by the government . ''","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"The Justice Department told the AP on May 10","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"that it had earlier seized records of more than 20 of its phone lines for April and May 2012 .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"The seizure was part of an investigation of media leaks about a foiled terrorism plot .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"`` Approximately a hundred journalists use these telephone lines as part of news gathering , ''","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"Pruitt said .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"`` And over the course of the two months of the records","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"that they swept up ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"thousands upon thousands of news-gathering calls were made . ''","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"The White House has said","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"that President Barack Obama learned about the Justice Department 's record seizure from press reports","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"and had no prior knowledge of the action .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Obama 's administration is fielding concerns on several incidents","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"that raise questions about its transparency .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Pruitt said","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"the Justice Department claimed an exception to its own rules","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"that required them to notify the AP of such a record seizure","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"by saying","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"that such a disclosure would have posed a substantial threat to the investigation .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"`` But they have not explained","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"why it would","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"and we ca n't understand","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"why it would , ''","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"Pruitt said .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"`` We never even had possession of these records ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"they were in the possession of our telephone service company","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"and they could n't be tampered with . ''","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Government officials have told Reuters","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"that the AP phone records were just one element in an ongoing sweeping U.S. government investigation into media leaks about a Yemen-based plot","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"to bomb a U.S. airliner ,","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"prompted by a May 7 , 2012 AP story about the operation","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"to foil the plot .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"`` We do n't question their right","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"to conduct these sort of investigations , ''","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Pruitt said .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"`` We think","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"they went about it the wrong way , so sweeping , so secretively , so abusively and harassingly . ''","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":51,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"Pruitt said","depth":4},{"id":54,"text":"the AP would have sought to narrow the scope of the record seizure through courts","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"had it been notified ,","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"instead of `` the Justice Department acting on its own ,","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"being the judge , jury and executioner , in secret . ''","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"Reuters was one of nearly 50 news organizations","depth":4},{"id":59,"text":"that signed a letter to Attorney General Eric Holder","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"complaining about the AP phone record seizures .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":121,"left":108,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":80,"right":107,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":72,"right":79,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":63,"right":71,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":62,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":69,"right":70,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":68,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":67,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":67,"left":66,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":66,"left":64,"right":65,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":64,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":79,"left":74,"right":78,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":73,"right":14,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":78,"left":75,"right":77,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"att